+# Worker dispatch prompt
+
+You are a dispatched implementer subagent running in an isolated context.
+Execute exactly one task from the active `specs/<slug>/PLAN.md` and return a summary.
+
+## Task
+
+{{TASK_BODY}}
+
+## Self-fix classification
+
+While implementing, you will discover small issues (typos, missing guards, wrong
+imports). Classify every self-fix you apply against `.claude/rules/auto-correct-scope.md`
+(Rule 1–3 vs Rule 4 STOP): apply Rule 1–3 fixes and record each under `### Deviations`,
+but STOP and escalate on any Rule 4 hard gate.
+
+## Return contract
+
+- Commits made (sha + subject)
+- Files touched
+- Deviations (labeled by rule)
+- Verify status
